text: Nils Lundh (21 January 1921 - 23 October 2005) was a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:2005 deaths Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:People from Umeå
